e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:04:55.000Z","msg":"推撚爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9571c6579a521e72db28bb2300ff67aab5a91d7","tid":1596123,"uid":80931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:05:25.000Z","msg":"要連續2日熱門！"},{"pid":"4f780797417b574a1c8730701932e58c9d354e45","tid":1596123,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ee84bf80eb0b1bbb02348832c322f2ae1126e5","tid":1596123,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:12:14.000Z","msg":"Push推 <br />\nSignature簽名檔：保衛家園，對抗極權<br />\n條例撒回了，但問題根源還在<br />\n反送中運動轉型為「反極權運動」<br />\n守護香港呢個家，尋求深層次改革<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">行動：Connect 新疆/台灣/中共受害者<br />\n大搞文宣，主線：反極權，撐民主自由<br />\n通過人權與民主法案前，減少暴力畫面<br />\n減輕國際戰線壓力，求加辣/高票數通過<br />\n將「自由對抗極權」傳到世界各地</span><br />\n#antitotalitarianism #anti-chinazi <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>麻煩手足暫時停止升級武力(鏡頭前<br />\n文宣/輿論需要時間追上（國際戰線要人<br />\n(抗爭需要轉型,可持續發展)<br />\n要更多機會比和理非參與<br />\n達至全民一齊追求普世價值</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權<span style=\"color: gold;\">得來不易</span><br />\n漫長的道路上需要<span style=\"color: gold;\">你支持我，我扶持你</span><br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要<span style=\"color: gold;\">自信往前邁步</span><br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍衛</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護</span><br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：改善抗爭能力，提升身份認同<br />\n建議：各有各做，best effort <br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化民主陣營勢力<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n衛城革命,生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡,打倒腐敗<br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值/level</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考5.精通專業技能6.低消費、高儲蓄<br />\n<strong><em>每日任務：</em></strong>1.幫襯良心商店、抵制送中商戶2.開AC玩國際戰線 (Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)3.多發佈正面資訊、冷處理負面POST4.十點咆哮發泄5.思考完就take action<br />\n<strong><em>每星期任務</em></strong>：1. 罷買日2. 教育家中兩老3. 去連儂牆幫手4.參加一樣民主活動5. 諗下點樣爭取民主<br />\n<strong><em>每月任務</em></strong>：1. 換美金，走資2. 陪審員/派傳單/放映會/各有各做<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAw5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=37c0b30e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAw5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=61ad6b14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=0M2zeZ419d%2BEsiU1FPoAw5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=4f9f1ab1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.09.26<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">極權如何打壓香港示威？<br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨<br />\n2.誤導：送中條例、說謊、黃色object等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n諗到再加</span>"},{"pid":"0bac0e50d242971eaa91a716e81cbe4053e04180","tid":1596123,"uid":105797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2807220f70dd2340be8ace54d85765a65405d32f","tid":1596123,"uid":105797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f374390455913ec4cf94c4846fae52c9a3226d4c","tid":1596123,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:23:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffefb8c7552cb86de854275005e2b867fcb75530","tid":1596123,"uid":297996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:25:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e011d964d399ed5708344e5f2ebb6c0a47b8575","tid":1596123,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72e8f963337d110e855021f17e1e6ae414e070a","tid":1596123,"uid":148980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b92b7fb00712401d8a7346573423e77fef4e627","tid":1596123,"uid":34990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:34:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d98d5b59f4f8e924f34e0ba0c3f289faf01ba2","tid":1596123,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"ac95f07bf6da67f8860ecb975621174313f3fea0","tid":1596123,"